      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the magic. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh feeling every time you slide into the driver's seat. You might find a tiny speck if you\u2019re looking with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s as stunning as the day she rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for by a true enthusiast, you\u2019ve found it!",
      "price": 48500.0,
