      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level specimen of automotive engineering. This unit features a blueprint-balanced powertrain with zero parasitic loss, paired to a close-ratio transmission with crisp, positive engagement across all gates. The suspension geometry has been meticulously tuned for optimal roll-center correction, utilizing high-durometer bushings and adjustable damping rates for a surgical steering response. Every fluid interval has been strictly adhered to using high-viscosity synthetics to ensure thermal stability under load. The chassis rigidity remains factory-spec, showing no signs of fatigue or torsional stress. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically flawless platform that exceeds original factory tolerances. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector who demands peak volumetric efficiency and uncompromised structural integrity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
